        <h4 class="text-[20px] font-heading font-semibold text-white mt-8">2. Facility Construction & Design Oversight</h4>
        <p class="text-body text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Oversaw the end-to-end design & construction of <strong>custom-built bouldering walls</strong>, with an emphasis on:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-3 text-body text-white/80">
          <li>Well-designed physical layout to accommodate both <strong>technical climbers</strong> and <strong>first-timers</strong>, optimizing spatial flow and customer experience.</li>
          <li>Craftsmanship quality</li>
          <li>Safety standards</li>
          <li>Modularity for route versatility</li>
        </ul>

        <img 
          src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/rXrwu3C1AgdX4CSjJE6wyeEoa4.jpg?width=4032&height=3024" 
          alt="Construction Process"
          class="w-full rounded-lg my-8"
        />

        <h4 class="text-[20px] font-heading font-semibold text-white mt-8">3. Brand Development & Community Building</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-3 text-body text-white/80">
          <li>Created a strong <strong>visual identity and messaging system</strong> for Boulder Box Saigon.</li>
          <li>Positioned the brand as <strong>approachable, creative, and community-first</strong>—distinct from more commercial gyms.</li>
          <li>Launched a <strong>PT program</strong> with certified coaches, which achieved a <strong>100% return rate</strong> in its first year.</li>
          <li>Organized <strong>over three climbing events</strong>, drawing <strong>160+ participants</strong>, helping to organically grow brand presence.</li>
        </ul>

