        </div>

        <h4 class="text-[20px] font-heading font-semibold text-white mt-8">4. Business Development & Growth Strategy</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-3 text-body text-white/80">
          <li>Directed <strong>sales, pricing strategy, and customer acquisition efforts</strong>, resulting in <strong>250% year-over-year sales growth</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Rapid word-of-mouth traction</strong> within the local expat and youth fitness community</li>
          <li>Implemented scalable business operations, including <strong>booking, memberships, merchandise, and private coaching</strong>.</li>
          <li>Implemented scalable group climbing coaching framework to collaborate with schools, universities and colleges.</li>
        </ul>

